suliten isasa’ay a aazihan cudad taneng malangat uzumaay IP puenengan saca misaungayay a mikawaway-kalumyiti tungus.
izaw dada’ saka mitena’ mipeci’, atu matatungus [[{{MediaWiki:Policy-url}}|pasayzaan saca amikuwanay-pasayzaay]] a zasatu sasa misaungay.
piisasa’ suliten cacay masaheciay a mahicaay（tinaku: kilul ku kumu cacay mapapeci’ay a kasabelih）.
kapah kisu pisaungay [//ais.wikipedia.org/wiki/ inayi’ kakuniza subal luyou CIDR]kamu-sakilul kese milangat IP subal, satabakiay mahasa a subal IPv4 ku /$1, IPv6 ku /$2.

izay IP puenengan nu misu mawawah kutay sefu-kikay, sisa malangat tuway.
pitakus situngusay tu kawaw nu calay-zazan(wanglu) nu misu saca mikumi sitaneng midama, sakamuen tu heni tina mangaleb pihaceng kazahkezan a munday.

softblockrangesreason: IP puenengan nu misu ($1) inayi’ mahasa paceba pangangan paanin, pipatalabu.

IP puenengan nu misu pisaungay X-Forwarded-For satangahan, kisu saca pisaungay nu misu a kutay sefu-kikay malangat tuway.

lockdbtext:

piluceki amahica kisu haw? zumasatau imahini midiput tu kawaw pahezek sa mihulak nasulitan-sulu a pamutek.

pilucek kisu amahini kisu haw?

unlockdbsuccesssub: misipu pamutek tu sulu nu kalunasulitan tuway

mamutek tu ku nasulitan-sulu.
amana kapawan anu mahemin midiput pahezek [[Special:UnlockDB| mihulak pamutek ]] nasulitan-sulu.
lockfilenotwritable:
inayi’ tungus suliten nasulitan-sulu pamutek tu tangan.
calay-belih(wangyi) sefu-kikay maydih tu tangan a suliten tungus u azihen atu mihulak pamutek nasulitan-sulu.
movepagetext: isasa’ay a aazihan cudad kapah sapihica miliyaw pangangan cacay kasabelih, atu milimad mikabu kya kasabelih a sacahamin nazipa’an nasulitan ta izaw baluhay kalungangan a kasabelih. maluman pyawti a kasabelih amiliyaw patatuzu’ kasabelih, payiza pisaungay baluhay pyawti a kasabelih. pikinsa izaw haw ku [[Special:DoubleRedirects|hatusa miliyaw patatuzu’]] saca [[Special:BrokenRedirects|malepi’ay a miliyaw patatuzu’]] maydih misumad. izaw kisu sikining ngay masasiket palalid payiza tatenga’ay a kakitizaan. piazihen, amahica baluhayay a kasabelih kalungangan masaungay tuway, kyu tina kasabelih caay malimad tu zuma kakitizaan, anu caay baluhay kalungangan miliyaw patatuzu’ kasabelih zumasatu inayi’ amahicahica mikawaway-kalumyiti nazipa’an. mahiza sakamu, kapah kisu milimad mungangaw ta zuma kalungangan a kasabelih patiku ta saayaway kalungangan，uyzasa amana mitahpu amahicahica tu ayzaay kasabelih. azihen: tina saungay sakay manamuhay kasabelih hakay tadamaan atu talibahalay a sumad; iayaw nu saungay kaluceki matineng kisu haw hakay kya teluc nay milimad.
movepagetalktext:
amahica mipili’ tina atilad, mahizaay a sasukamu kasabelih amalunuk atu tina belih maladay milimad ta baluhay kakitizaan, ihekal sibaluhay kalungangan izawtu cacay muenengay sasukamu kasabelih.
uyniyay a pulita, amahica izaw siceyo kanca kisu lima-saungay milimad saca mikabu tu izaway a kasabelih.

exporttext:
kapah kisu patahkal matuzu’ay kasabelih saca kayadah belih a sulit atu mikawaway-kalumyiti nazipa’an, pisaungay XML kese a tabu.
uyniyay tangan kapah pacumud ta zuma pisaungay  MediaWiki a Wiki, micaliw [[Special:Import|pacumud kasabelih]].

apatahkal kasabelih, isasa’ nu sulit atilad misulit kasabelih pyawti, cacay pyawti pisaungay cacay tusil, zumasatu pipili’ apatahkal ayzaay a sumad yamalyilu haw sacahamin nazipa’an masumad nu ayaway nasulitan, saca patahkal dada’ ayzaay a sumad atu sazikuzay mikawaway-kalumyiti a cesyun。

i sulit atilad kapah tu kisu pisaungay masasiket, tinaku:[[{{#Special:Export}}/{{MediaWiki:Mainpage}}]] dayhiw patahkal kasabelih "[[{{MediaWiki:Mainpage}}]]"
exportcuronly: yamalyilu dada’ ayzaay a sumad nu ayaway, caay yamalyilu lekuay a sumad nu nazipa’an
exportnohistory: piazihen:zayhan matalaw tu sefu-kikay silahciay munday, mapasatezep tu patahkal ku kasabelih a sacahamin nazipa’an misilit.
